column2: Water is brownish red.  Partly cloudy.  Heavy rain on June 15- 1997 late afternoon and evening.
Water reddish brown- cloudy- cold and windy.
Lake very low.  No rain for 2+ weeks.  Warm sunny.
Partly cloudy- 70 degrees- great day.  There was a lot of rain the past two weeks.
Cloudy and the temperature is 65 degrees.
Sunny and 80 degrees.  Water temp 70 degrees.
James Tiry- Robert Illian And Ken Speich
